1. *Stare*, moje uspomene su dragocene. (My *old* memories are precious.)

2. On je najstariji od nas. (He is the *oldest* of us.)

3. Ona je veoma *stara* žena. (She is a very *old* woman.)

4. *Stari* grad je prekrasan. (The *old* town is beautiful.)

5. Ja ću morati da kupim *stari* automobil. (I will have to buy an *old* car.)

6. Oni su *stari* prijatelji. (They are *old* friends.)

7. Ja volim da čitam *stare* knjige. (I like to read *old* books.)

8. Moja baka je još uvek veoma *stara*. (My grandmother is still very *old*.)